            sourceSnippet: '\'Scold me more\': IU tearfully apologises to fans amid Perfect Crown backlash on her birthday — Gulf News',
            source2: 'Straits Times',
            sourceUrl2: 'https://www.straitstimes.com/asia/east-asia/south-korean-singer-iu-targeted-in-online-trolling-over-election-disruption',
